{
    "tiddlers": {
        "$:/language/Import/Upgrader/Tiddler/Duplicate": {
            "created": "20180301083553942",
            "text": " Duplicate Title",
            "bag": "default",
            "revision": "1",
            "type": "text/vnd.tiddlywiki",
            "title": "$:/language/Import/Upgrader/Tiddler/Duplicate",
            "tags": "",

        },
        "$:/plugins/tesseract/ImportResolution/ImportResolution.js": {
            "created": "20180301083528020",
            "text": "/*\\\ntitle: $:/plugins/tesseract/dragSnippetTitle/ImportResolution.js\ntype: application/javascript\nmodule-type: upgrader\n\nUpgrader module that if there are existing tiddlers with same title as inccoming tiddler\n\n\\*/\n\n(function() {\n\t/*jslint node: true, browser: true */\n\t/*global $tw: false */\n\t\"use strict\";\n\n\texports.upgrade = function(wiki, titles, tiddlers) {\n\t\tvar self = this,\n\t\t\tmessages = {};\n\t\t// Check for tiddlers on our list\n\t\t$tw.utils.each(titles, function(title) {\n\t\t\tvar existingTiddler = wiki.getTiddler(title);\n\t\t\tif (\n\t\t\t\texistingTiddler &&\n\t\t\t\texistingTiddler.hasField(\"plugin-type\") == false\n\t\t\t) {\n\t\t\t\tmessages[title] = $tw.language.getString(\n\t\t\t\t\t\"Import/Upgrader/Tiddler/Duplicate\"\n\t\t\t\t);\n\n\t\t\t\tvar tiddler = new $tw.Tiddler(tiddlers[title], {\n\t\t\t\t\ttitle: wiki.generateNewTitle(title),\n\t\t\t\t\tcaption: title\n\t\t\t\t});\n\t\t\t\ttiddlers[tiddler.fields.title] = tiddler.fields;\n\t\t\t\ttiddlers[title] = Object.create(null);\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t});\n\t\treturn messages;\n\t};\n})();\n",
            "bag": "default",
            "revision": "1",
            "type": "application/javascript",
            "title": "$:/plugins/tesseract/ImportResolution/ImportResolution.js",
            "tags": "",
            "module-type": "upgrader",
            "modified": "20180301083755820"
        },
        "$:/plugins/tesseract/ImportResolution/ImportWarning": {
            "created": "20180301083611336",
            "text": ".tc-import tbody td:nth-child(3)  {\ncolor:red\n}",
            "bag": "default",
            "revision": "1",
            "type": "text/css",
            "title": "$:/plugins/tesseract/ImportResolution/ImportWarning",
            "tags": "$:/tags/Stylesheet",
            "modified": "20180301083812882"
        },
        "$:/plugins/tesseract/ImportResolution/Readme": {
            "created": "20180301084329079",
            "text": "Original title is added as caption",
            "title": "$:/plugins/tesseract/ImportResolution/Readme",
            "tags": "",
            "modified": "20180301084346929"
        }
    }
}
